article.description: — John Knight III posted 16 points as Southern Utah narrowly defeated Utah Valley 60-56 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Knight III leads S. Utah past Utah Valley 60-56
article.linkText: Knight III leads S. Utah past Utah Valley 60-56
article.story: CEDAR CITY, Utah -- — John Knight III posted 16 points as Southern Utah narrowly defeated Utah Valley 60-56 on Wednesday night. Maizen Fausett had 15 points for Southern Utah (6-3), which earned its fifth straight victory. Fardaws Aimaq had 18 points and 10 rebounds for the Wolverines (7-2), whose seven-game win streak ended. Connor Harding added 15 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
